text: Jacqueline Jane White (born November 27, 1922) is an American actress. She is best known her appearances in Crossfire and The Narrow Margin. She worked for both MGM and RKO in the 1940s and 1950s. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:American stage actors Category:Actors from Beverly Hills, California
